'''Sola Sobowale''' (yin jiji to 26 Awewesun 1963) bo yin aihundatọ [[Naijilia|Naijilia]] tọn, aihunkantọ tele tọn, anadenanutọ podọ nubayitọ. Sola Sobowale lẹzun omẹ nukundeji tọn to 2001 to aihun paa de he yin didohia to tele ji mẹ Super Story: Oh Father, Oh Daughter.

