4.1	Aihundatọ
4.2	Nubayitọ

==Azọn==
Whẹpo e do lẹzun omẹnukundeji tọn de, Sola Sola Sobowale tindo ada etọn to aihun The Village Headmaster, Mirror in the Sun podo aihun ayọgbe
